    <entry>
      <title>IntelliJ IDEA的试用破解</title>
      <link href="/2022/03/11/hello-world/"/>
      <url>/2022/03/11/hello-world/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>IntelliJ IDEA. IDEA 全称 IntelliJ IDEA，是java编程语言开发的集成环境。. IntelliJ在业界被公认为最好的java开发工具，尤其在智能代码助手、代码自动提示、重构、JavaEE支持、各类版本工具 ( git 、 svn 等)、JUnit、CVS整合、代码分析、 创新的GUI设计等方面的功能可以说是超常的。</p><h2 id="教程（本方法支持且仅支持idea-2021-2版本以前的idea工具）"><a href="#教程（本方法支持且仅支持idea-2021-2版本以前的idea工具）" class="headerlink" title="教程（本方法支持且仅支持idea 2021.2版本以前的idea工具）"></a>教程（本方法支持且仅支持idea 2021.2版本以前的idea工具）</h2><h3 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">如果在这之前你的idea已经过期或使用过激活码，请完全卸载后再使用此插件</span><br><span class="line">idea 2021.2下载链接：https://pan.baidu.com/s/1g2iiY0zsU-xWc4uNoAh0LQ </span><br><span class="line">提取码：apex</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="一-使用插件压缩包"><a href="#一-使用插件压缩包" class="headerlink" title="一.使用插件压缩包"></a>一.使用插件压缩包</h3><h4 id="1-下载"><a href="#1-下载" class="headerlink" title="1.下载"></a>1.下载</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">重置包链接：https://pan.baidu.com/s/16HW0fVUJTFavcx7jYt22Yg </span><br><span class="line">解压密码apex</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="2-安装"><a href="#2-安装" class="headerlink" title="2.安装"></a>2.安装</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">打开idea,中间会先弹出一个注册框，我们勾选 Evaluate <span class="keyword">for</span> free, 点击 Evaluate， 先试用30天.</span><br><span class="line">先随便建个 Java 工程， 然后将网盘中最新的 IDEA 无限重置 30 天试用期补丁 ide-eval-resetter-2.1.6.zip拖入 IDEA 界面中</span><br><span class="line">点击accep进行安装</span><br><span class="line">安装完毕后点击about</span><br><span class="line">点击Eval Reset</span><br><span class="line">在下方弹出框里勾选Logout when reset 和Auto reset before per reset</span><br><span class="line">点击Reload后点击Reset重置等待idea重启完毕即可</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-在idea的应用商店里下载重置插件"><a href="#2-在idea的应用商店里下载重置插件" class="headerlink" title="2.在idea的应用商店里下载重置插件"></a>2.在idea的应用商店里下载重置插件</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1.导入plugins.zhile.io方法</span><br><span class="line">进入File--&gt;Settings--&gt;Plugins</span><br><span class="line">点设置（齿轮符号）--&gt;Manage Plugin Repositories...</span><br><span class="line">点小加号（+）--&gt;输入：plugins.zhile.io</span><br><span class="line">2.下载插件</span><br><span class="line">进入File--&gt;Settings--&gt;Plugins，点Marketplace</span><br><span class="line">搜：Ide Eval Reset</span><br><span class="line">找到Ide Eval Reset，点击installed下载</span><br><span class="line">加载完成后点击OK！</span><br><span class="line">3.刷新时间</span><br><span class="line">进入Help--&gt;Eval Reset</span><br><span class="line">点击“Reset”按钮重置时间</span><br><span class="line">4.检查一下</span><br><span class="line">打开Help--&gt;Register，显示”30 day left“就ok了。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
